StateMachine
Class State

java.lang.Object
  StateMachine.State
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<State>
public class State
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<State>, java.lang.Cloneable

A state consists of a status, a message, a callable Call-Object which is called on entry and a Map mapping other States to Commands.

Author:
XTFIWS
